<h1>
  Food and drink festivals
</h1>

<p>
  Hello {{data.owner.name}},
</p>
<p>
  Thanks for registering your interest with our food and drink festivals. This is 
  not a booking confirmation. We'll still need to do the official stuff later.
</p>
<p>
  This is a copy of the things you told us you need. We have a copy too, so 
  hopefully nothing gets missed.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>
  Your business
</h2>
<p>
  Exhibitor name:<br>
  {{- data.business['exhibitor-name'] -}}
</p>
<p>
  Type of products:<br>
  {{- data.business['type-of-products'] -}}
</p>

<hr>

<h2>
  Your contact details
</h2>
<p>
  Name:<br>
  {{data.owner.name}}
</p>
<p>
  Phone:<br>
  {{data.owner.phone}}
</p>
<p>
  Email:<br>
  {{data.owner.email}}
</p>
<p>
  Address:<br>
  {{data.owner.address}}
</p>
 
<hr>

<h2>
  Events you want to attend
</h2>
{%- for event in data.eventsAttending %}
<h3>
  Event {{loop.index}}
</h3>
<p>
  Event details:<br>
  {{event.name}}<br>
  {{event.location}} {{event.date}}
</p>
<p>
  Requested items:<br>
  {%- for item in event.requestedItems -%}
    £{{item.cost}} {{item.name}}<br>
  {%- endfor -%}
</p>
<p>
  Estimated cost:<br>
  £{{event.estimatedCost}}
</p>
{%- endfor -%}
